name: Fab Four Gear Genesis VIP Pass

metadata.name: FFG Genesis VIP Pass 1
metadata.description: Fab Four Gear is an NFT project consisting of over 100 3D/360 scanned, extremely rare and period-correct instruments just like the ones the Beatles used before their maniacal success. No treasure of this magnitude sits in one collection except ours. And our 4444 unique Genesis VIP Passes is our introduction into the NFT metaverse where our story begins. Drop by drop, up close and personal, the world will not only get to see our coveted acquisitions, but will have the opportunity to own all of them as NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. And for every drop, we will have unknown artists, musicians, and photographers collaborate with famous contributors to showcase their collective masterpieces as NFTs to the world. But, it’s not just about our collection, it’s about sharing yours with us so we can all thrive and be on full display for the world to see.  Everyone gets a chance to shine at FAB FOUR GEAR, and we can’t wait to do it together.
